ues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader/issues/new?body=module:%20shopinvader_api_customer%0Aversion:%2016.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- ACSONE SA/NV\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Benjamin Willig \\<<mailto:benjamin.willig@acsone.eu>>\n- Quentin Groulard \\<<mailto:quentin.groulard@acsone.eu>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is part of the [shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader](https://github.com/shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader/tree/16.0/shopinvader_api_customer) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_api_customer.tests", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_api_customer.tests.test_shopinvader_customer_api", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_api_customer.tests..test_shopinvader_customer_api", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_api_customer.tests.test_shopinvader_customer_api", "documentation": ["Copyright 2024 ACSONE SA/NV", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_api_customer.tests.test_shopinvader_customer_api.TestShopinvaderCustomerApi", "bases": ["FastAPITransactionCase"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_api_customer.tests.test_shopinvader_customer_api.TestShopinvaderCustomerApi.setUpClass", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "cls", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo